le and secondary social studies teachers' political knowledge and a content analysis of CNN Student News.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aPolitical sciencexStudy and teaching (Secondary)xUnited StatesxUnited States. 0aPolitical sciencexStudy and teaching (Secondary)zUnited States. 4aEducation : Curriculum. 4aEducation : Education. 4aEducation : Teaching and Learning. 4aPolitics and Law : Politics. 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846771940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438467719423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438467719/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles